{"type": "article", "id": 27048, "title": "Nike 与切尔西签十年期合约，以及，星巴克配色球鞋不错｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。\r\n", "date": "2016-05-19T10:40:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 27841, "name": "BFC/GQ"}, {"id": 25325, "name": "男装设计师"}, {"id": 27842, "name": "大奖赛"}, {"id": 1027, "name": "彩妆"}, {"id": 796, "name": "球鞋"}, {"id": 1618, "name": "赞助"}, {"id": 755, "name": "足球"}, {"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 873, "name": "星巴克"}, {"id": 27581, "name": "For Love & Lemons"}, {"id": 4029, "name": "American Eagle"}, {"id": 23444, "name": "The Body Shop"}, {"id": 11702, "name": "Craig Green"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 71, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702133807OcqPeg5JTxUXYLV1.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Urban-Outfitters-reports-surprise-rise-in-first-quarter-comparable-sales,694335.html\"><b>Urban Outfitters 一季度销售额增长</b></a>｜服装集团 Urban Outfitters 一季度同店销售额获得增长，旗下 Anthropologie 及 Urban Outfitters 品牌需求正逐渐恢复。周三宣布一季度收入上涨了 10.5% 超出预期，净销售额增长 3.2% 至 7.626 亿美元。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/American-Eagle-appoints-Kyle-Andrew-as-EVP-Chief-Marketing-Officer,694338.html\"><b>American Eagle 任命新执行副总裁</b></a>｜American Eagle  近日宣布将由 Kyle Andrew 担任执行副总裁、首席市场官，6 月 6 日生效，此前她在 Kate Spade 工作，最近升至高级副总裁及 Kate Spade Saturday 的品牌总监。2002 －2007 年间她担任 Gap 市场部门副总裁。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Nike-and-Chelsea-sign-87-million-apparel-deal,694360.html\"><b>Nike 与切尔西俱乐部签下十年赞助合约</b></a>｜美国媒体报道，上周刚刚与 adidas 解约的切尔西俱乐部，近日与 Nike 达成最新的赞助合约，每季 8700 万美元的高价标志这一合作成为欧洲足坛第二大商业赞助，仅次于 adidas 与曼联十年支付 13 亿美元的合约。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/media-news/digital/tk-bfc-gq-designer-mens-wear-fund-10432856/\"><b>Craig Green 获得 BFC/GQ 男装设计师基金奖</b></a>｜近日，英国时装协会（British Fashion Council）宣布英国设计师 Craig Green 获得 2016 年 BFC/GQ 男装设计师基金大奖，毕业于中央圣马丁的 Craig Green  2012 年创立自己的同名品牌。这一英国最大的男装奖项还将为 Craig Green 带来 15 万英镑的奖金。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/The-Body-Shop-appoints-global-make-up-artist-Lisa-Houghton,694264.html\"><b>The Body Shop 聘用彩妆艺术家</b></a>｜The Body Shop 周三宣布将聘请英国美妆大师 Lisa Houghton 担任品牌全球美妆艺术家。在此职位上，Houghton 将与 The Body Shop 在产品开发、潮流、创造季节性妆容——指导视频及数字内容制造等层面上合作。此前 Houghton  常出现在 Vogue、 W Magazine、Harper’s Bazaar 等杂志上，合作过的名人包括 Taylor Swift、Jennifer Lawrence、Scarlett Johansson 等。</p>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p class=\"\">手工皮革品牌 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/5/roberu-leather-phone-case-for-iphone-se\">Roberu 为 iPhone SE 推出了皮质手机套</a>，看起来很有质感，售价在 77 美元左右。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133752mo6CXRdjYcHAGyxu.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133753cXgUH8E1Z3KJR4lk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133753TmA2fGEYBqRMN7P9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070213375467YejLHq4RI3C9dQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/5/supreme-the-north-face-steep-tech-spring-summer-2016-collection-delivery-2\">Supreme 和 The North Face 2016 年春夏联名</a>第二波上线：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133754Df5PozuE3YS7GXRJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133755FruUZ67a4AeLf0vt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133755E7FcU01AuphQvyLa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133756ZDLRrdfkbIQ5GK6c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070213375683cbV7fdwjBqTWDL.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">Nike SB 推出<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/5/nike-sb-dunk-low-premium-starbucks\">星巴克配色版本的 Dunk Low</a>：<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133757cvtIEaGKz9sAfpwk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">Shopbop 最新的<a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/love-lemons-spring-2016-dresses-shopbop/\"> lookbook，叫做“Garden Party”</a>， 拍摄  For Love &amp; Lemons 品牌的春季系列裙装：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133757AQFpsYwg96Bkz5cG.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133758ci1o3JUFDKAXr7nP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.1375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021337595vQyJ7lb62xm0AoN.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.07125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133759v8q4CDza5prYZhXf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">喜欢以上风格的，应该会觉得 For Love &amp; Lemons 最新的泳装系列也不错：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133800E0znbUGw421KX7dY.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133800M73E4UuKJVYisLTk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133801wNsMicbLhDxe7rd0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133802HrD0pNf6sq4XVtdL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133802EvXcdFVQYS8i2psm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/5/publish-brand-2016-summer-collection\">Publish Brand 推出春夏系列男装</a>，黑白、橄榄绿及大地色系为主：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133803R7ahfzpwSEDTn9vG.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133804aj5PfL6tlFOncyoH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133804AXLRqpg9Na0bV4FQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133805xnKyJLpDRBlU03jM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021338056F28IdUrH0uMoBK5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133806XWRhbf2KEpuHkoLj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133806DifkmBd4AQWx9bOS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>